Usage:

To generate a pedigree file:
'java -Xmx6g -jar VCF2LR.jar -d <directory with .vcf formated files or a single .vcf file> -g <Genotype_Counts.txt> -o <pedigree_output_name>'

To visualize the pedigree for a pedigree text file ped.txt:
'Rscript plot_pedigree.R <pedigree_output_name.txt>'

The output will be created: pedigree_output_name.pdf

See:
https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5408770/
